        <updateDate>2018-12-04T16:40:54Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Options Markets Stability Act</b></p> <p>This bill&nbsp;revises the method of calculating the risk, for purposes of&nbsp;satisfying capital rules applicable to depository institutions and depository institution holding companies,&nbsp;of&nbsp;certain options cleared through a central counterparty. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
